        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "I have a sister, or shall I say I had a sister... Her name was Anaralia, a powerful Mystic such as myself. Until she met with an untimely demise. While travelling through Mirkwood forrest. Her curiosity got the better of her. And she found a passage to the central south of the forrest. *shudders a moment*"
