        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "Ah the worse is to come. The poison and twisted magic of the spiders has made her into an undead Mystic of terrible power. She has all the strengths of the spiders and all the strengths of her previous life as a mystic. Anaralia must be stopped before she gains more power. Even now she plans to rally the spiders to seek more followers. She seeks to raize Lake Town."
